{{{NNTP_MIME_POSTS	FUD_OPT_3	512
Format forum messages as MIME encoded posts before sending them to a newsgroup. If disabled, messages will be UUencoded.}}}

{{{DISABLE_WELCOME_EMAIL	FUD_OPT_3	2048
